room_title: Escape room "The Magician's Secret" by Unlock The Adventure in Titusville
room_description: Step into a magical world where things may not be as they seem and there are clues and surprises to discover all around you! Experience a journey into the magician's inner sanctum complete with special effects and highly-interactive puzzles! Work together as a team in this fun and exciting game and get lost in the magic as you search for the one and only... Magician's Secret!
